# game/script-a3-shizune.rpy:6876
translate pt_br aside_and_ahead_2_d99102f1:

    # mi "It was in the student council room, you know. When it was just the two of us."
    mi "Foi na sala do conselho estudantil. Quando eramos só nós duas."

# game/script-a3-shizune.rpy:6878
translate pt_br aside_and_ahead_2_d28b7c1c:

    # mi "I had these fantasies of Shicchan staying alone in the office, trying to put everything together all by herself. It seemed so lonely to me, and so sad~. I think I wanted it to be that way~."
    mi "Eu tinha essas fantasias da Shizunezinha estando sozinha no escritório, tentando arrumar tudo por si mesma. Parecia tão solitário para mim, e tão triste~. Acho que eu queria que fosse daquele jeito~."

# game/script-a3-shizune.rpy:6880
translate pt_br aside_and_ahead_2_03d06757:

    # mi "That way, I could be there for Shicchan, and maybe Shicchan would like me. Even though there was no reason for me to believe it, I did anyway. I wanted it to be true, so I was okay with letting myself believe it, even though I think I knew."
    mi "Desse jeito, eu poderia estar ali pela Shizunezinha, e talvez a Shizunezinha gostaria de mim. Mesmo não tendo razão para eu acreditar, eu fiz do mesmo jeito. Eu queria que fosse verdade, então estava tudo bem para mim em me deixar acreditar, apesar de eu pensar que já sabia."

# game/script-a3-shizune.rpy:6882
translate pt_br aside_and_ahead_2_4847df1e:

    # mi "That day was really, really~ beautiful, too, Hicchan~. We were done with everything, and I was looking out through the window. Even through the window, the light was so warm~… I wanted to stay like that forever, next to Shicchan."
    mi "Aquele dia foi muito, muito~ bonito também, Hisaozinho~. Nós tinhamos terminado tudo, e eu estava olhando para fora da janela. Mesmo através da janela, a luz era tão quente~… Eu queria ficar daquele jeito para sempre, próxima à Shizunezinha."

# game/script-a3-shizune.rpy:6884
translate pt_br aside_and_ahead_2_803e9d33:

    # mi "But~! Then I looked at Shicchan, and she had her back to the window and was still working on something, blocking out the rest of the world. The light was on her shoulders, like when I would put a blanket on my shoulders as a little kid."
    mi "Mas~! Então olhei para a Shizunezinha, e ela estava de costas para a janela e ainda trabalhava em algo, ignorando o resto do mundo. A luz estava sobre os seus ombros, como quando você põe um cobertor sobre os ombros quando criança."

# game/script-a3-shizune.rpy:6886
translate pt_br aside_and_ahead_2_33f39c86:

