# game/script-a3-shizune.rpy:6888
translate pt_br aside_and_ahead_2_4031a423:

    # mi "Shicchan looked… hm~… It was like, Shicchan looked in a way that made me want to be with her… But it felt like it would be hard for that to happen."
    mi "Shizunezinha parecia… hm~… É como se, a Shizunezinha parecesse de um modo que me fazia querer estar com ela… Mas parecia que isso seria muito difícil de acontecer."

# game/script-a3-shizune.rpy:6890
translate pt_br aside_and_ahead_2_7e23a276:

    # mi "Wahaha~. That was~, a really~ long~ time ago. My hair was different back then, too. A little messy~? I cut it because Shicchan was always talking about it."
